text: Daggubati is an Indian name that may refer to * Daggubati Purandeswari, Indian politician *D. Ramanaidu (Daggubati Ramanaidu 1936–2015), Indian film producer. * Daggubati Suresh Babu, Telugu film producer and managing director of Suresh Productions * Daggubati Venkatesh, Indian film actor * Daggubati Venkateswara Rao, member of the Indian National Congress * Rana Daggubati, Indian film producer, visual effects co-ordinator, photographer and actor ==See also== *Daggubati-Akkineni family Category:Surnames of Indian origin
title: Daggubati
